OL,3,CFirst picture of mother who killed her
OL,4,Ctwo children and stabbed her husband
OL,6,FThis is the first picture of Veronique
OL,7,FJohn, 50, of Flax Street, Stoke-on-
OL,8,FTrent who was found by a jury to have
OL,9,Fkilled her two young children in knife
OL,10,Fattacks described by a judge as
OL,11,F"almost too horrific to comprehend."
OL,13,FJohn killed Ethan and Elizabeth at
OL,14,Ftheir home in June 2023 before going
OL,15,Fon to attack her husband, Nathan, at
OL,16,Fthe car wash where he worked.
