OL,6,FElizabeth, 7, was pronounced dead at
OL,7,Fher home having suffered a fractured
OL,8,Fskull and knife wounds, while the 50-
OL,9,Fyear-old's son, Ethan, 11, suffered
OL,10,Fmore than 20 sharp force injuries.
OL,12,FThe wounds to John's son were "almost
OL,13,Fas if" she was trying to decapitate
OL,14,Fhim, the judge said.
