OL,3,CFirst picture of mother who killed her
OL,4,Ctwo children and stabbed her husband
OL,6,FJohn was found to have carried out the
OL,7,Fattacks during a "trial of the facts"
OL,8,Fas she was deemed unfit to stand trial
OL,9,Fdue to mental illness. She has been
OL,10,Fdiagnosed with complex post-traumatic
OL,11,Fstress disorder as well as personality
OL,12,Fand depressive disorders.
OL,14,FShe has been given an indefinite
OL,15,Fhospital order for the "frenzied and
OL,16,Fheinous" attacks.
OL,18,FThe court heard that she killed the
OL,19,Fchildren to avoid her husband having
OL,20,Fthem.
