OL,6,FMr Justice Choudhury told John: "You
OL,7,Fclaim that you are not a monster...
OL,8,Fbut your acts were either those of a
OL,9,Fmonster or someone who has lost all
OL,10,Fcapacity to reason.
OL,12,F"It's clear that by the time of the
OL,13,Ftrial you were not fit to plead. It
OL,14,Fhas been conclusively determined that
OL,15,Fyou did kill your own children and
OL,16,Fmake an attempt to kill Nathan."
