OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read to
OL,7,Fthe court by prosecutor Peter Grives-
OL,8,FSmith, Mr John, who was stabbed
OL,9,Fshortly after his children were
OL,10,Fattacked, said his wife had "viciously
OL,11,Fand brutally" taken their lives.
OL,13,FMr John said: "On June the 11th my
OL,14,Fwhole world was turned upside down. I
OL,15,Flost the two most important and
OL,16,Fprecious persons in my life at once."
