OL,6,FEthan and Elizabeth had
OL,7,F"instantaneously and undeservedly"
OL,8,Flost their lives, Mr John said, adding
OL,9,Fthat it was horrific that one of the
OL,10,Fsiblings may have witnessed the other
OL,11,Fbeing "put to death in a beastly
OL,12,Fmanner".
OL,14,FDetective Chief Inspector Cheryl
OL,15,FHannan, from Staffordshire Police
OL,16,Fsaid: "This case was distressing for
OL,17,Fall involved, it was traumatic for the
OL,18,Flocal community and has left so many
OL,19,Fpeople devastated by what happened.
