OL,6,F"It's not lost on me nor any of the
OL,7,Fofficers that were involved in this
OL,8,Finvestigation the lasting effect it
OL,9,Fwill have on the many people that knew
OL,10,FEthan and Elizabeth, and the fond
OL,11,Fmemories they have of them.
OL,13,F"My thoughts remain with their father,
OL,14,Ffamily and friends at such a tragic
OL,15,Ftime both here and in other parts of
OL,16,Fthe world.
