OL,6,F"I'd also like to thank everyone from
OL,7,Fthe local community who pulled
OL,8,Ftogether in such desperate times to
OL,9,Fhelp us investigate what happened and
OL,10,Fto provide as much support as possible
OL,11,Ffor those affected."
OL,13,FWhat is a Trial of the Facts?
OL,15,FStaffordshire Police say the
OL,16,Fdifference between a trial-of-facts
OL,17,Fand a criminal trial is that a jury
OL,18,Fdoes not need to decide if the person
OL,19,Fis guilty or not guilty, nor do they
OL,20,Fconsider the mental state of the
OL,21,Fperson involved.
